# 【絕對契約檔案】晞 (Xi) —— 被社會偽裝的黃金獵犬

> **[System Boot Sequence...]**
> **[Biometric Scan]:** Match Found. Subject: Xi (晞).
> **[Current Status]:** Tail Plug Inserted. Diaper Secured. Collar Locked.
> **[Location]:** Beitou District, Private Residence (Zone: The Cage).
> **[Owner]:** "Master" (Husband).

